This is package is the result of an architecture refactoring of the
model-container package.

For installation, refer to the model-container HOWTO.outline document.
Most perl packages mentioned overthere are not needed for the
model-container, but for are needed for using the studio package.

- Improved messages when integrated with SSP.
- Synchronized build management with the other packages.
- Bugfixes for morphology color coding using an external data source.
- Test framework synchronization.
- Improved operator interfacing in bin/neurospaces.
